hackathon-description-text: FIVR hackathon is a weekend long event for people interested in virtual reality and augmented reality to share ideas and come together to craft experiences with the latest VR platforms and gadgets.
hackathon-rules: You are completely free to hack whatever you want during the weekend! However, we also have some topics provided by event partners and organizations.
hackathon-description-header: It's the time for the first FIVR hackathon!
